---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About TechGear</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="mb-6">
        Welcome to TechGear, your premier destination for cutting-edge technology and gadgets. Since our founding in 2025, we've been committed to bringing you the latest and most innovative tech products from around the world.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Our mission is to make high-quality technology accessible to everyone. We carefully curate our product selection to ensure we offer only the best in each category, from audio equipment to gaming peripherals.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Quality Guarantee</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Every product in our store undergoes rigorous testing to ensure it meets our high standards for quality and performance. We stand behind every item we sell with our satisfaction guarantee.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Expert Support</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Our team of tech experts is always ready to help you find the perfect product for your needs. Whether you're a gaming enthusiast or a professional creator, we've got you covered.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Visit Our Store</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        123 Tech Street<br>
        Silicon Valley, CA 94025<br>
        United States
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 8:00 PM<br>
        Saturday: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br>
        Sunday: Closed
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>